## SwiftPM
.build/
.swiftpm/
*.xcodeproj
*.xcworkspace
DerivedData/

## WebAssembly — ignore generated modules EXCEPT the committed test fixtures,
## the bundled Example demo module, and fixtures-src sources. The large
## regenerable guest modules (e.g. NetworkingGuest.wasm) stay out of git; the
## small committed fixtures are force-added by the patterns below.
*.wasm
!Tests/**/*.wasm
!Examples/**/*.wasm
!fixtures-src/**/*.wasm

## macOS
.DS_Store
